			h2 Focus outline

			p Generally, outlines have been replaced with borders (with some exceptions). However, all focus states for all elements should use a 2px yellow border.

			img(src="#{dir}images/outline-example.svg")

			pre
				code.language-css
					| /* Remove outline */
					| outline: none;
					| border: 2px solid @heritage-yellow;
			pre
				code.language-css
					| /* Improve outline */
					| outline: 2px solid @heritage-yellow;
